      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your existential crisis is a natural response to the vastness and indifference of the universe. It's almost... refreshing to acknowledge the futility of our existence. And yet, it's precisely this awareness that can give you a sense of freedom from the burdens of expectation and responsibility. By recognizing the impermanence of our accomplishments, you can let go of the need to achieve or be remembered, and simply exist in the present moment.",
